{
  "stem": "4963.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Everything was laid out, and the governess would come in, and you have to do this, and you have to do that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And take us to school with our little lunch pail.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I just rebelled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was really-- always rebellion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, anyhow, so we were living in the-- we were marched into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And within about two months, there was the [NON-ENGLISH], what we used to call them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They dug, in the seventh fort or ninth fort, they dug great big holes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they immediately drove all of us out into the street, into the street in the [NON-ENGLISH] in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the Germans-- I remember them to this day-- went around and said, right, left, right, left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Right meant survival, and left meant death.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My, my cousin Liena Prensky, Paula's, Aunt Paula's daughter was immediately-- my aunt was a very smart and bright woman.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she thought, well, perhaps she would send this 20-year-old with her boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She had a boyfriend, and they were both pictures of health.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she thought perhaps they would be spared, you know, to see two young, beautiful people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Of course, they needed them for work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But unfortunately, it, it was, did not happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They, they were standing in line.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So she sent my cousin Liena off with her boyfriend to stand in the lineup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they were separated, and the whole family was killed together with my 20-year-old cousin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And my Aunt [NON-ENGLISH] never forgave herself for that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So that was a big blow in our family, because she was really the first one and, and, I must say, the only one who was killed during the ghetto years.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were all outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
